		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>A lifebinder follows a religious practice dedicated to protecting or nurturing life. They are powerful healers, more so than any others, and are often the difference between life and death for an adventuring party. Some may dedicate themselves formally to healing, whereas others might just be dedicated to spiritual practices centered around protecting or nurturing a community.​​</em></p><table><caption><p>The Lifebinder</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.lazdJ4HirsqixWY8]{Blessed Healing}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.SI4GOzETULz4hkoF]{Channel Divinity: Preserve Life}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.PLIwCIGPl0DnyhoJ]{Infused Healer}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.43O2lpH8Va14CKr9]{Healing Overflow}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.1yHTY47oEvbPoqw8]{Supreme Healing}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Cleric Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Extra Spells</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.I80JFUFkSDeMFgXF]{Cure Wounds}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.HKiFSQzi9E2rgaLV]{Healing Word}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.gQCBKxTyZeqCvy0D]{Lesser Restoration}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.UoEQtWyLpJr5ZbGd]{Prayer of Healing}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.cZLKEokFoqKN8dqR]{Mass Healing Word}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.6yixBp8pwhVAkbUJ]{Revivify